metadata.name: Luv-chan in Yuki-chan costume
metadata.description:
Luv-chan x CryptoMaids collaboration Fanart.
Thank you so much, Luv-chan & CryptoMaids!

The costume is arranged for Luv-chan. I matched the coloring and sleeve shape to her.
She is on the huge sneaker box.
